{"tid":2497927,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"IP大戰｜中國IPv6地址數量超美國   專家：將來一人一IP 監控更容易","createTime":"2021-04-20T23:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T02:10:31.000Z","uid":204533,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d38d9392c3cb04cee46bde64fa2a6dc2c8f632ad","tid":2497927,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T23:31:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210421/2RYXERE2C5CHZM5VGBGK4P23UA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210421%2F2RYXERE2C5CHZM5VGBGK4P23UA%2F&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ1IIeLT5oGwh5bXtaSRQp68%3D&h=387e5bd2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210421%2F2RYXERE2C5CHZM5VGBGK4P23UA%2F&h=c9004602\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210421/2RYXERE2C5CHZM5VGBGK4P23UA/</a>"},{"pid":"bae5dbad2ccda43295286ea422eb94d75ac7d856","tid":2497927,"uid":204533,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T23:34:25.000Z","msg":"//每個接入互聯網的設備，都需要一個IP地址，之前是使用IPv4，但因其IP資源不足，限制互聯網的應用和發展，於是互聯網工程任務組（IETF）設計出了IPv6，以作取代。所謂IPv6，就是指互聯網協議第六版（Internet Protocol version 6），IP數量比IPv4多得多，IPv4可供給全球最多40幾億個IP，IPv6的IP數量則增加了2的96次方倍，號稱可以給地球上的每粒沙子分配一個IP地址。//<br />\n<br />\n//截至今年4月8日，中國總共獲得IPv6地址塊數量為59,039個／32（即是每段32位元的IPv6地址數目），目前排名第二的美國擁有57,785個／32。//<br />\n<br />\n//不過，IPv6的應用，引發私隱問題引發爭議。<span class=\"red\"><strong>2017年11月，中共中央辦公廳、國務院辦公廳發佈《推進互聯網協議第六版（IPv6）規模部署行動計劃》時，中國電信科技委員會主任韋樂平就曾指出，從國家安全的角度看，<span class=\"xx-large\">IPv6引入後能達到一人一個IP，實名制就可以真正實施了</span>，這在相當程度上為中國網際網路的安全管理提供可靠的保證。</strong></span>//"},{"pid":"ce75900ebac5346ffa6b0eeaa8cf78b55411797b","tid":2497927,"uid":155095,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T23:35:27.000Z","msg":"養大中共呢隻魔鬼嘅係西方國家<br />\n<br />\n而家中共有咗錢要反噬西方國家<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/0_5AtSKVhwCEZu9gV7_VmqVy_1200x0.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=ht